asreml.output

Class Yhts

  • java.lang.Object
    • asreml.output.AsremlOutputFile
      • asreml.output.Yhts

  • public class Yhts
extends AsremlOutputFile
    Class to read in the Asreml Yht file which is a file that contains y^ values, residuals, etc for the model that was run. The results are stored into a Map with the record index as the key and the Yht as the value.
    Author:
    Scott Smith
    See Also:
